<title type="html"><![CDATA[custom PowerPak mapper]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6872&amp;p=66342#p66342"><![CDATA[
When prgain(15:0) matches 6000-7FFF make prgbankin(18:13) (input to "prgchrsize" module) be { 4'b0000, wrambank }. wrambank is 2 bits for 8K*4 = 32K.<br /><br />E: BTW I think the PRG size for the ROM has to be at least 32K to access all of the 32K WRAM because prgchrsize module masks the address.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=80">thefox</a> — Fri Aug 20, 2010 10:47 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
